<p>Select <strong>Manual upload</strong>, <strong>FTP</strong>, <strong>HTTPS</strong> or <strong>SFTP</strong>.<br>
Depending on the selected option, the following settings are displayed:</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Manual upload</strong> = Select and upload a local file.<br>
After running an import, the file is automatically deleted from the webspace. This is preset by default. In order to save the file you need to remove the check mark. <strong><em>Note:</em></strong> storing the file on the webspace is subject to a fee.</p>
</div>
