<h2 id="900">10. Viewing the export history</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>Setup » Markets » PIXmania » Export history</strong> menu, you can see an overview of the export history of your PIXmania items. Export histories <strong>in progress</strong> as well as <strong>completed</strong> export histories are displayed here.</p>
</div>
</div>
